  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out whether elective sigmoid resection will improve
      quality of life compared to conservative treatment with lifestyle guidance and fiber
      supplement in patients with a recurrent or complicated diverticulitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
